author: Maria Armental
title: Oprah Winfrey Sells Some Shares in Weight Watchers International
text:
Oprah Winfrey, the most public face in the turnaround of Weight Watchers International Inc., has sold some of her shares and donated a small portion to her charitable foundation.
In all, the changes amount to nearly one-quarter of her holdings, according to a securities filing Tuesday.
